Application.Domain

Class Vision

  • java.lang.Object
    • Application.Domain.Vision

  • @Entity
public class Vision
extends java.lang.Object
    Vision is the class that maps the database Entity Vision. A Vision is a representation of the thoughts of the User on a Scenario.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Corti Lorenzo, Tocchetti Andrea
